.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-INVOICE-PAID-AMOUNT-TOTAL-MONTHLY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-invoice-paid-amount-total-monthly \- FEAT-2876 node-invoice-paid-amount-total-monthly
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-invoice-paid-amount-total-monthly
.SH DESCRIPTION
Total paid invoice amount received this calendar month (FEAT-2876).
.PP
Queries all invoices via lightning-cli listinvoices and sums amount_received_msat
for invoices with status=paid whose paid_at timestamp falls within the current
UTC calendar month.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
